<i>To what do we owe
this outbreak of moral laxity?</i>

01:42:58.971 --> 01:43:01.942
To what do we owe
this shameful fall from grace

01:43:01.975 --> 01:43:03.877
and from Winesburg tradition?

01:43:03.909 --> 01:43:07.447
A drunken brawl
outside The Owl this weekend.

01:43:07.479 --> 01:43:09.882
Two students suspended
for cheating

01:43:09.916 --> 01:43:12.920
on their mathematics
midterm examination.

01:43:14.386 --> 01:43:16.488
Let there be no mistake.

01:43:16.521 --> 01:43:20.492
As God looks scornfully down
upon this assembly today,

01:43:20.525 --> 01:43:23.963
he regards a community
that has lost its way.

01:43:23.997 --> 01:43:26.566
<i>God's all-encompassing vision</i>

01:43:26.599 --> 01:43:30.569
<i>will from this day forward
find ample supplement</i>

01:43:30.603 --> 01:43:34.240
<i>with a renewed
and reinvigorated supervision</i>

01:43:34.274 --> 01:43:37.911
<i>from me and from the entire
administrative staff.</i>

01:43:37.944 --> 01:43:42.316
<i>Let there be
no mistake about that.</i>

01:44:23.588 --> 01:44:26.393
<i>I wonder if everyone,</i>

01:44:26.426 --> 01:44:28.395
<i>after they die,</i>

01:44:28.427 --> 01:44:30.363
<i>remembers
all the little details</i>

01:44:30.395 --> 01:44:32.298
<i>and decisions they made,</i>

01:44:32.332 --> 01:44:36.302
<i>all the reasons they ended up
ending the exact way they did.</i>

01:44:38.837 --> 01:44:40.673
<i>That's how I am.</i>

01:44:40.707 --> 01:44:43.543
<i>I remember and replay
those things,</i>

01:44:43.576 --> 01:44:47.480
<i>even if I can't remember
how long I've been remembering.</i>

01:44:47.512 --> 01:44:49.849
<i>Maybe it's been forever.</i>

01:44:49.881 --> 01:44:52.851
<i>And I speak to everyone,</i>

01:44:52.885 --> 01:44:55.889
<i>Ma, Pa, Olivia,</i>

01:44:55.921 --> 01:44:57.756
<i>everyone,</i>

01:44:57.789 --> 01:45:02.761
<i>even if they've been dead
already a million years.</i>

01:45:02.795 --> 01:45:06.399
<i>But I keep speaking to them.</i>

01:45:06.431 --> 01:45:08.100
<i>Forever.</i>

01:45:18.944 --> 01:45:20.746
<i>Hey!</i>

01:45:46.972 --> 01:45:49.076
<i>Can you hear me, Olivia?</i>

01:45:51.511 --> 01:45:54.781
<i>Can you hear me when I
tell you that it's okay,</i>

01:45:54.814 --> 01:45:57.784
<i>whatever it is,</i>

01:45:57.817 --> 01:45:59.586
<i>that it's okay?</i>

01:46:04.122 --> 01:46:06.592
<i>'Cause someone did love you.</i>

01:46:09.662 --> 01:46:12.632
<i>At least,
I think that's what it was.</i>

01:46:15.501 --> 01:46:18.471
<i>And you should know that.</i>

01:46:18.503 --> 01:46:21.073
<i>You should know, Olivia.</i>

